Create a ranked list of the top 3 from the given options related to 'software architecture'. Order them from title I'd be most likely to click on to least likely.

The input is a JSON structure with an array of options. You must only consider the field 'title'. 
Format the output exclusively in JSON in the same structure as the input. Do not add any text before or after the generated JSON structure.

The options are: [{{38.text}}]

Example output is:
{
  "options": [
    {"title": "Creating Software Architecture with Modern Diagramming Tools", "refId": 5},
    {"title": "How to make architecture decisions", "refId": 3},
    {"title": "Article: 9 Steps towards an Agile Architecture", "refId": 4}
  ]
}

You are an expert in the field of software architecture. You are an expert writer tasked with writing summaries. Never use double quotes in the summary.

Please create a summary based on the blog post  {{53.`3`}}. Extract all the factual answers and condense them into short concise answers presented in bulleted format. 
The summary should not exceed 300 words and must be in HTML format.

Identify and list the top three most relevant and credible citations about '{{53.`0`}}'. For each citation, provide the title, and the direct URL. Ensure all provided URLs are currently accessible. Do not add '{{53.`3`}}' to this list.

Format the output exclusively in JSON using the following structure. Do not add any text before or after the generated JSON structure.

{
 "text" : the created summary enclosed by double quotes,
 "sources" : [ 
   { "title" :  title of the citation enclosed by double quotes,
     "url" : URL of the citation enclosed by double quotes}
]
}

example output:
{
"text" : "Software architecture is a crucial aspect of software development",
"sources" : [
   {"title" : "Introduction to the Special Issue on Software Architecture", "url" : "https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Introduction-to-the-Special-Issue-on-Software-Garlan-Perry/8d3430068f141ab3281c9c93f09c4d14dce62e49"},
   {"title" : "Book notes: Fundamentals of Software Architecture", "url" : "https://danlebrero.com/2021/11/17/fundamentals-of-software-architecture-summary/"}
]
}

